.wrapper
  .reg
    .reg__header
      .reg__logo
        img(src="./img/logo.svg" alt="favbet logo")
      p.reg__text Welcome Bonus
      .reg__bonus
        .reg__money 
          span.reg__up up to
          span.reg__sum 225 000 ₴
        .reg__fs 300 FS
    .reg__players
      picture
        source(media="(max-width: 1032px) and (min-height: 1032px) and (orientation: portrait)" srcset="img/players.png")
        source(media="(max-width: 1024px)" srcset="img/players-512.png")
        source(media="(max-width: 1280px)" srcset="img/players-640.png")
        source(media="(max-width: 1440px)" srcset="img/players-720.png")
        source(media="(min-width: 1441px)" srcset="img/players-960.png")
        img(src="img/players-640.png" alt="favbet players")
    p.reg__footer * Bonus means the opportunity to receive a prize as part of the “Welcome bonus” Promotion.
      | Details on the website favbet.ua. Promotion dates are from 01.09.2024 to 31.12.2025. 
      | The bonus is available for new customers only.